text: Wenzu Vella (5 March 1924 - 27 April 2003) was a Maltese sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Maltese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Malta Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics
